data.description: This beautiful 3bd 1ba home is newly renovated and ready to move in! There's hard wood floors throughout house. Kitchen and Bathroom fully renovated with Ceramic Tile finish.  Equipped with all NEW Appliances and Private Fenced In Yard. Close to Public Facilities, minutes from Frankford Transportation Center and  walking distance to Stetson Middle School. I95 Highway within 5mins driving distance. Wissinoming Recreation Park only a block away, treeline park featuring grassy areas, sports fields, a kids playground and a seasonal splash pass.  Aria Health is also less then a mile away from property.
